        "data": "<h1 class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">Service Updates for Liferay Cloud</h1>\n<p>The services update for 1/24/2023 is a patch revision bump for <strong>backup</strong><strong>,</strong> <strong>database, and CI</strong> services. </p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2>DXP Cloud Stack - 1/24/2023</h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 727px; float: left; height: 350px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 98.8333px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 102.383px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Previous Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 101.3px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Current Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 379.483px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Docker Images</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 98.8333px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Backup</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 102.383px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.0.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 101.3px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.0.1</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 379.483px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>liferaycloud/backup:5.0.1</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 98.833